TOPIC 10:
REACTIONS OF METALS WITH OXYGEN-REACTIVITY SERIES FOR METALS
DURATION: 6 Periods
GENERAL OBJECTIVE: By the end of this topic the learner should be able to arrange metals in order of their reactivity with oxygen and
apply the principles to different situations.
